cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL

The paper deals with multimodal data retrieval, which involves computer vision (image-text pairs) and natural language processing (video-tag pairs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of fuzzy logic, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves computer vision techniques such as image processing and feature extraction (cs.CV) and natural language processing techniques such as text analysis (cs.CL).
